95
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] Šta da ja sad s ovim radim?

96
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je ono ta nelagodnost.

97
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,080
